{"tid":1633634,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開][反思]從大學生角度話你知點解大學罷課失敗","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T01:08:01.000Z","uid":148983,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b278f42277bb9b801d918f2586da97f57041ef76","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>講嘅只係其中一間大專嘅個人觀察，其他大專可能有唔同，歡迎補充<br />\n利申ShittyU，恥與為伍</strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n好多人都不停屌點解大專學生成日唔響應罷課，除咗暴大其他大專又好似冇咩聲氣咁，有見及此，小弟決定出post分析同解釋下點解大專罷課雷聲大雨點少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 本地生人數不足</span></ins></strong><br />\n冇錯，第一日罷課好多人去咗百萬大道集會好曡馬，但大家忘記咗呢度係咁多大專合計人數，其實諗返轉頭其實咁多大專先咁多人好似唔係非常多咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實上，讀大專嘅人會知道現時大學充滿非本地生，大專校園充滿外國人同中国人，即使本地大專生全部黃去罷課都未必會真正影響到課堂進行（而事實上小弟見過有藍嘅大專生） <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 教授</span></ins></strong><br />\n喂，教授都關事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇錯，正正就係教授出曬事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟就讀於一間好中意打飛機嘅大專，校長長期唔見人，喺爵士過身先出現，平時搵個藍絲副校出緊急通告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試問一個連政治同生活無法分割都唔明，叫人唔好將政治帶入校園嘅校長點會理學生吖，起碼隔離暴大校長都肯出嚟拍下檯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺一個咁嘅環境下，由於年年要刷Rank打飛機所以有好多非本地教授來往，莫講非本地知道咩事又支持我哋嘅教授，本地黃嘅更加少之又少。人哋整個要求100%出席率嘅課程，你叫大專生唔上，等於斷送自己GPA <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你會話GPA又如何，但大佬吖我都想畢業㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 宣傳嚴重不足</span></ins></strong><br />\n之前大家都略有所聞大專發起兩星期罷課，坦白講我同身邊朋友都淨係知道開學頭兩日罷課（後來查證得知頭兩日只係指中學生，唔係大專生），心理上冇準備，加上本地+非本地嘅教授+學生好多都唔知到罷課兩星期，更唔知我哋罷課原因，導致冇支援 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來追查發現學生會出咗篇聲明就冇下文，由此可見文宣嚴重不足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">大專罷課成功方程式</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">校舍貼滿文宣&gt;人肉解釋&gt;多學生響應&gt;教授支援=罷課成功</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">從來冇唔夠文宣，只係冇人貼，傳送門：</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4oCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=0f188378\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a></span>"},{"pid":"478cadfba28b0832b158b18557abc70f6f66fdc8","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"631186aeac888a03ec8236eda86d0d0d54740216","tid":1633634,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但黨鐵而家咁撚樣你都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cee950f3c3d5bf42187d267033d5e2c2d43260","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"adce462dadfe0727f875da1d4da25f677b05aebf","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"ff9ab6ca53f0fe92e232da0811500589fae70877","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"6199c687058233a441011ff205505b0925df4d54","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"ae78c1407e76b515a6a84997c36485bbbcb41fa2","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"d17821b0d5a85b0ef8efff5b0eb8620d34fd372d","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:45:14.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"8e25132b75027124288e2db3c532904fab067396","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"3b2d2fef95eb7e8f20b5cc13fe7f41ea66b0aa0c","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"0f889782964c6196eabd3ab5f494d8235f0ee1a6","tid":1633634,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:46:42.000Z","msg":"推到有心嘅大學生睇"},{"pid":"30d99d74d8d2e980f764a2c5b6edff7c5bcda446","tid":1633634,"uid":30834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a4757164682f958e99aa28d398d209183b530b","tid":1633634,"uid":210254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"1. 但本地生多過內地生，罷課人數得幾十個都無，唔好同我講一間學校得幾十個本地生<br />\n2. 「可能你會話GPA又如何，但大佬吖我都想畢業㗎」 你上少幾堂就就畢業唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 有好多次罷課講咗好耐 包括9月頭罷課"},{"pid":"00e3d2deb4f81f4a5bde76af3576c1fbdfc29ef7","tid":1633634,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4oCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=cdc98dd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"41f2451c7e86915da67b077579272ecb902e3470","tid":1633634,"uid":37719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"番工同中小學都係某程度上「強制」參與者出席<br />\n<br />\n而大學本身都一堆人走堂，個上堂模式太過於自由，有D垃圾堂本身都已經得三幾隻nds係度支撐住，所以走開堂既已經擺緊<br />\n上開堂既就覺得就算走左間課室既光景都係一鳩樣<br />\n那怕無人出席，個prof仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37fe61c18a1808610ee5cad20052a7692e0b7fe","tid":1633634,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"Shitty罷唔罷都係咁垃圾架啦"},{"pid":"22f6a5fd4085bb2881c98f03df99455e5f5651e8","tid":1633634,"uid":230256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:02:07.000Z","msg":"根本唔關事 每間大學都應該係有6成以上係香港人 不過每次罷課都淨係得嗰幾十個 不過我眼見嘅大學生 多數都係黃 可能覺得罷課無用 或者驚影響gpa所以唔罷"},{"pid":"d3f3ffb5099bb08ba16f8228a471bad742630fe5","tid":1633634,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKzRiec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKzRiec.png&h=0a69efe9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99dc24b6ba45e6127174b10a4d4b4df41ca69366","tid":1633634,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:30.000Z","msg":"其實淨係attendance計分都罷唔到啦"},{"pid":"9f11b9bf223626272e2b14432dc3d996f6d50955","tid":1633634,"uid":82309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:09:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d545a516079058a9e18601d869e8867296c038","tid":1633634,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:54:22.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229dc1cb88cfac1808f42064c5fa4f47bee1c6b7","tid":1633634,"uid":80413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:55:27.000Z","msg":"各大專院校巴絲 不如一齊搵自己校長<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644941</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷課再加組隊搵校長有無得諗"},{"pid":"10d524bd95687d4cafe2b6a804116072b7aea9c3","tid":1633634,"uid":305357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:45:57.000Z","msg":"要人！科大要科大人！！<br />\n班nds推左個黨員選入校董會<br />\n選到既話佢地諗住收窄學生會既權力<br />\n之後滲多啲自己人入去，定啲措施幫助ust大陸人<br />\n<br />\n讀緊科大嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644115</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n班大陸人靜靜雞係wechat吹哂雞去左投票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地係朋友圈推得好行，但好似冇咩local留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9ec40246251c773b37dbccae50861686f4e3b7","tid":1633634,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"根本既差別係，當年雨傘大家罷課，就可以去佔中，主要及唯一戰線<br />\n依家罷完無訂去，又唔係日日有夢發"}]}